<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>مَا لَا يَنْقُضُ الوُضُوء<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج١ص٤٦:</span> وَقَالَ أَبُو هُرَيْرَةَ: <span class="c2">«لاَ وُضُوءَ إِلَّا مِنْ حَدَثٍ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>